Brice Beckham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brice_Beckham 0 James Brice Beckham (born February 11, 1976 in Long Beach, California) is an American actor most famous for his role as Wesley T. Owens in the television sitcom Mr. Belvedere and for his role as Corey in I Hate My 30's. He currently lives in Los Angeles and is a member of LA's Namaste theater group.
